column5: Someone suggested that I should post a link to this thread here as there are apparently some OFC members in the photo's. I hope they're right.  http://www.hookmorefish.com/phpBB/viewtopic.php?t=1709  Cheers,
right on!  thats a helluva an 'eye there Birdee is holding
WOW........  looks like you guys had a blast,and thats a real nice walleye,the pics & reports are great as well

Thanks fishindevil, it was a great weekend. Unfortunately, due to beer related injuries, my mate and I woke up a little late on the Sunday and didn't get on the water until 9.30am, missing the early bite  Cheers,
Great pics! There are some big smiles there!!
you didn't think it was so bad when you were enjoying some wobbly pops though ... glad we share the same views on a certain fishing show host
LOL!  It was great meeting you guys, I would imagine there were a few sore heads in your group the morning too  Cheers, Shaun
Awesome report and pics.  You must of had a great time everyone. Those darn wobbly pops.  Good thing I only drink Rye LOL!!!!!!1
